			Everyone else answered the rest, but as per #5, you can run in little circles, about the size of the circle in the center of the Guild hall.. Actually it is the size of the guild hall circle thing, ebcause i was able to perfectly run on the outside edge of it over and over.<br><div><br>Simply by pressing and holding up and left/right key at the same time, and hitting enter once and letting go of all keys, will let you do this. You will need to hit enter again to close the chat box, because the chat box opens up, though.<br><br>You can also autorun backwards by holding down the down arrow and hitting enter. Same with forward with the forward key, but there is numlock for that (default key).<br><br>Someone above me posted 3rd party is legal as long as it does &quot;ALTER&quot; the gameplay information back and forth... right and wrong. 3rd party is illegal on programs such as *insert program name here* which is a program outside of game with a built in map and shows where the mobs in the zone are. That isnt legal, and will get you banned. Stuff such as outside MP3 players, instant messengers, etc as listed above in another post, are legal.<br></div><div></div>	
